Deprecated API

Contents

Deprecated Classes
retrofit.ChangeableServer
          Implement Endpoint to change URL and name at runtime. This class will be removed in version 1.5. 
retrofit.Server
          Use Endpoints.newFixedEndpoint(java.lang.String). This class will be removed in version 1.5. 
 

Deprecated Methods
retrofit.RestAdapter.Builder.setServer(Server)
          Use RestAdapter.Builder.setEndpoint(String) or RestAdapter.Builder.setEndpoint(Endpoint). This method will be removed in version 1.5. 
retrofit.RestAdapter.Builder.setServer(String)
          Use RestAdapter.Builder.setEndpoint(String) or RestAdapter.Builder.setEndpoint(Endpoint). This method will be removed in version 1.5. 
 

Deprecated Constructors
retrofit.client.Response(int, String, List
, TypedInput)
          Use Response.Response(String, int, String, java.util.List, TypedInput). This class will be removed in version 1.5.
